  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Faith_of_the_Seven\" title=\"Faith of the Seven\"><img alt=\"Star of the Faith.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/9/91/Star_of_the_Faith.svg/50px-Star_of_the_Faith.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/9/91/Star_of_the_Faith.svg/75px-Star_of_the_Faith.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/9/91/Star_of_the_Faith.svg/100px-Star_of_the_Faith.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Septa</span><br />Maryam</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Faith_of_the_Seven\" title=\"Faith of the Seven\"><img alt=\"Star of the Faith.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/9/91/Star_of_the_Faith.svg/50px-Star_of_the_Faith.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/9/91/Star_of_the_Faith.svg/75px-Star_of_the_Faith.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/9/91/Star_of_the_Faith.svg/100px-Star_of_the_Faith.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Maryam_by_feelenum.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Maryam by feelenum.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/1/19/Maryam_by_feelenum.jpg/300px-Maryam_by_feelenum.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"371\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/1/19/Maryam_by_feelenum.jpg/450px-Maryam_by_feelenum.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/1/19/Maryam_by_feelenum.jpg/600px-Maryam_by_feelenum.jpg 2x\" /></a><div>Maryam by feelenum</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Septa\" title=\"Septa\">Septa</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiances</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Faith_of_the_Seven\" title=\"Faith of the Seven\">Faith of the Seven</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Targaryen\" title=\"House Targaryen\">House Targaryen</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Westeros\" title=\"Westeros\">Westerosi</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Died</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/54_AC\" title=\"54 AC\">54&#160;AC</a><br /><a href=\"/index.php/Dragonstone\" title=\"Dragonstone\">Dragonstone</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Maryam</b> was a <a href=\"/index.php/Septa\" title=\"Septa\">septa</a> at <a href=\"/index.php/Dragonstone\" title=\"Dragonstone\">Dragonstone</a> and a member of Princess <a href=\"/index.php/Rhaena_Targaryen_(daughter_of_Aenys_I)\" title=\"Rhaena Targaryen (daughter of Aenys I)\">Rhaena Targaryen</a>'s household.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabbirth.2C_death.2C_and_betrayal_under_king_jaehaerys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabbirth.2C_death.2C_and_betrayal_under_king_jaehaerys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Character\">Character</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Maryam&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Character\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Septa Maryam was considered young in <a href=\"/index.php/54_AC\" title=\"54 AC\">54&#160;AC</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabbirth.2C_death.2C_and_betrayal_under_king_jaehaerys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabbirth.2C_death.2C_and_betrayal_under_king_jaehaerys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Maryam&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Septa Maryam was one of <a href=\"/index.php/Rhaena_Targaryen_(daughter_of_Aenys_I)\" title=\"Rhaena Targaryen (daughter of Aenys I)\">Rhaena's</a> newer companions at the time of her death in <a href=\"/index.php/54_AC\" title=\"54 AC\">54&#160;AC</a>. At first, it was thought she had died of an <a href=\"/index.php/Illness\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Illness\">illness</a>. Later, it was revealed that she had been <a href=\"/index.php/Poison\" title=\"Poison\">poisoned</a> with the <a href=\"/index.php/Tears_of_Lys\" title=\"Tears of Lys\">tears of Lys</a> by Rhaena's husband, <a href=\"/index.php/Androw_Farman\" title=\"Androw Farman\">Androw Farman</a>, who was jealous of Rhaena's friendships with her ladies and weary of their mockery toward him.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabbirth.2C_death.2C_and_betrayal_under_king_jaehaerys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabbirth.2C_death.2C_and_betrayal_under_king_jaehaerys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Rhaena much lamented her death, and Septa <a href=\"/index.php/Edyth\" title=\"Edyth\">Edyth</a> was sent to <a href=\"/index.php/Dragonstone\" title=\"Dragonstone\">Dragonstone</a> in her place.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabbirth.2C_death.2C_and_betrayal_under_king_jaehaerys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabbirth.2C_death.2C_and_betrayal_under_king_jaehaerys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Maryam&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabbirth.2C_death.2C_and_betrayal_under_king_jaehaerys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabbirth.2C_death.2C_and_betrayal_under_king_jaehaerys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabbirth.2C_death.2C_and_betrayal_under_king_jaehaerys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabbirth.2C_death.2C_and_betrayal_under_king_jaehaerys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\">1.2</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabbirth.2C_death.2C_and_betrayal_under_king_jaehaerys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\">1.3</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, Birth, Death, and Betrayal Under King Jaehaerys I.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260405011708\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.087 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.450 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 781/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10579/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 7652/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 1521/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansi